@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@adminEmail = admin@bigsmoke.local
@adminPassword = admin123
@token =

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

### Configuracao publica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/config

### Lista produtos publicos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### Buscar produto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/moletom-classic

### Login admin
# Copie o token retornado e cole na variavel @token acima.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### Sessao admin atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Produtos admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Pedidos admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Analytics admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar pedido publico por codigo, numero ou session id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/public/BS-TESTE
